    "76400532-dfd5-4af3-89c6-7f237848dbf5": {
      "type": "text-only",
      "settings": {
        "large_text": "",
        "small_text": "<p>If you are as passionate about art as we are, we want to hear from you!  Here at Spectrum Noir encouraging<strong> emerging artists<\/strong> is very important to us. We want to create an inclusive community where everyone can share their work and find <strong>new inspiration<\/strong>. <\/p><p>That’s why we have designed our <strong>Community Gallery<\/strong>. It’s a space for you to showcase your artwork and take a look at what other aspiring artists are working on using their Spectrum Noir markers. If you would like to be in for a chance to feature your artwork in our gallery,<strong> just fill in this<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/e\/1FAIpQLSccaZakwrm5wdDr5xTXFZEUF9He3Dv-FUnQCHKqxqa_u0GZrw\/viewform\">online form. <\/a><\/p><p>We might even share your submissions on an email or on our social media pages. Don’t forget to share your<strong> Instagram handle<\/strong> so that our art community can check out the rest of your portfolio, and let us know which Spectrum Noir markers you have used to create your masterpiece!<\/p><p><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> The Spectrum Noir team works with many artists to showcase their skills. And it’s often artists like you who reach out to us, with suggestions to develop <strong>our markers to suit their needs!<\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Submit your artwork for our Community Gallery<\/strong> <\/p>",
        "link_text": "",
        "link_url": "",
        "left_align": false,
        "margin_bottom": "lg"
      }
    },
